<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>235</hymn_number>
<author>CDM Italia</author>
<title>Oh Happy Day</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Oh happy day, oh happy day
 When Jesus washed, oh when He washed
 When Jesus washed
 He washed my sins away.

[V2]
 He taught me how
 To watch fight and pray
 And live rejoicing in every day.</lyrics>
</song>